msgctxt "94\t155"
msgid "And stay down."
msgstr "Dónde estábamos..."

msgctxt "156\t202"
msgid "Going somewhere?"
msgstr "¿Jefecito?"

msgctxt "323\t448"
msgid "You know what, never mind!\\nYou can have your registry back!"
msgstr "¡Espera, ya entendí!\\n¡Te devolveré tu registro!"

msgctxt "442\t558"
msgid "Hm? I thought you said I gave it to you."
msgstr "¿Eh? ¿No dijiste que te lo había regalado?"

msgctxt "559\t627"
msgid "No need to hand it over now."
msgstr "No hay necesidad de devolverlo."

msgctxt "676\t798"
msgid "I'll just take it back\\nafter I smack the daylights out of you."
msgstr "Simplemente lo tomaré\\nluego de darte una paliza."

msgctxt "825\t950"
msgid "I'm sorry, you were right!\\nPlease don't smack me!"
msgstr "¡Lo siento! ¡Te lo suplico!\\n¡Por favor, no me golpees!"

msgctxt "980\t1049"
msgid "...Pitiful."
msgstr "Qué se le va a hacer..."

msgctxt "1058\t1192"
msgid "Fine. But instead, you're gonna tell me\\nwhy exactly you did all this."
msgstr "Bueno, pero a cambio me vas a contar\\npor qué hiciste todo esto."

